nodes.text: Classic Star Wars: A Long Time Ago...

Classic Star Wars: A Long Time Ago..., also marketed as Star Wars: A Long Time Ago..., is a comic series that is part of the Classic Star Wars series of comics and re-publishes the original Marvel Star Wars series.
It is featured in the Comics Link section of Star Wars Insider 61.
